In both cases, `max t₁.height t₂.height ≤ t₁.size + t₂.size`.
Adding 1 to both sides gives `1 + max t₁.height t₂.height ≤ 1 + t₁.size + t₂.size`.

Alternatively, since `t₁.height ≤ t₁.size` and `t₂.height ≤ t₂.size`, we have:
